snippet.title: Infinity Nikki - Gameplay Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
The open-world dress-up adventure game "Infinity Nikki" is about to start its PlayStation®5 beta test.

Venture into the vast Miraland to unravel the mysteries of "styling".
Alongside Nikki, awaken the magical powers hidden within various outfits and embark on a journey filled with fun.
See you in Miraland!
